<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">


    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body{
            font-family: "Poppins",sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #4f5ef1;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            color : #ffffff;
        }
    
        .message-sm {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-top: 50px;
        }
    
        .message-sm > h1 {
            font-size: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
        }
    
        .course-info {
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px 0px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px 2px rgba(239, 226, 226, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #000;
        }
    
        .course-info > h4 {
            color: #27d036;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-top: 0 !important;
            padding: 0 !important;
            font-family: "Poppins",sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
    
        }
        .course-name {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    
        .purchase-info {
            font-size: 16px;
        }
    
        .total {
            font-size: 18px;
           text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    
        .footer{
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 70px;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .footer > p > a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }
    
        .flex {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #9999993f;
        }
        .flex h4 {
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .flex.lg {
            width:85%;
            margin: auto;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .first-td {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color:#000;
            font-size: 16px;
            padding: 5px 0px;
            width: 1%;
            font-weight: 600 !important;
        }
        .second-td {
            font-weight: 500 !important;
            color:#000;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 16px !important;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            
        }
        td {
            padding: 10px;
            border: none;
            text-align: center;
            width: 28%;
        }
        td.col-2 {
            font-size: 16px;
            flood-color: #000;
            font-size: 500;
        }
        td.col-3 {
            font-size: 20px;
            flood-color: #000;
            font-size: 800;
        }
        .m-auto {
            width: 100%;
            margin: auto;
        }
        .table-row {
            width: 90%;
            display: block;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 10px 40px;
        }
    
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="message-sm">
            <h1>Your SecureStreamPro order is Confirmed!</h1>
            <p>Thank you for being part of our community..!</p>
        </div>
        <br>
        <br>
        <div class="course-info">
            <h4>Here's what you have ordered:</h4>
            <table style="border-bottom: 1px solid #0000002f;">
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        Order #: <%= order._id %>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        Order Date: <%= order.date %>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <table style="width: 90%; margin: auto; display: block;">
                <tr>
                    <td class="first-td">Item</td>
                    <td class="first-td">Cost</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <table style="width: 90%; margin: auto; display: block;">
                <tr>
                    <td class="second-td"><%= order.name %></td>
                    <td class="second-td"><%= order.price %> ₹</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <!-- <table class="table-row" style="border-top: 1px solid #00000029;">
                <tr>
                    <td class="col-2">Subtotal</td>
                    <td class="col-2"><%= order.price %> Rs.</td>
                </tr>
            </table> -->
            <table class="class-row" style="margin-top: -20px;">
                <tr>
                    <td class="col-3">Total</td>
                    <td class="col-3"><%= order.price %> ₹</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any queries, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:learnino17@gmail.com">khushalkumarkumawat5@gmail.com</a></p>
            <p>SecureStreamPro Team</p>
            <p>&copy; 2025 SecureStreamPro. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>